#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Episode 1 features 10 levels (including a secret level) of castle-storming action — no jumping, no looking up or down, pure shooting. id Software purchased the Wolfenstein trademark for just $5,000 in mid-April 1992, weeks before launch. Stealth gameplay features were removed late in development when John Romero found they slowed the game's pace. It runs on ECWolf compiled to WebAssembly."
msgstr "Episode 1 fitur tingkat 10 (termasuk tingkat rahasia) aksi serangan-kain - tidak melompat, tidak melihat ke atas atau ke bawah, penembakan murni. id Software membeli merek dagang Wolfhenstein hanya $5.000 di pertengahan April 1992, minggu sebelum peluncuran. Fitur gameplay Stealth dihapus akhir dalam pengembangan ketika John Romero menemukan mereka memperlambat kecepatan permainan. Ini berjalan pada ECWolf dikompilasi ke WebAssembly."

