#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake_shareware.html.heex:104
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "The \"Quake Guy\" was originally going to be a hammer-wielding warrior — the Lovecraftian theme was a late design change during development."
