msgstr "- 32 tingkat, Doom II kompatibel (BSD lisensi)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— 36 levels of open-source DOOM (BSD license)"
msgstr "- 36 tingkat membuka sumber DOOM (BSD lisensi)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:63
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— A Viking-themed total conversion with hand-drawn pixel art. Axes, bows, and runic magic. Freeware."
msgstr "- Sebuah Viking - bertema total konversi dengan gambar tangan pixel. Axes, busur, dan sihir unik. Freeware."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— A complete free replacement for DOOM II. 32 levels with the Super Shotgun. Compatible with community PWAD mods. BSD license."
msgstr "- Sebuah pengganti total untuk DOOM II 32 tingkat dengan Super Shotgun. Compatible with community PWAD mods. SIM BSD."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— A complete free replacement for Quake. Original levels, art, and music under BSD license."
msgstr "- Sebuah pengganti gratis lengkap untuk Quake. Tingkat asli, seni, dan musik di bawah lisensi BSD."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— A complete free replacement for Ultimate DOOM. 4 episodes, 36 levels with original art and music. BSD license."
msgstr "- Pengganti penuh untuk Ultimate DOOM. 4 episode, 36 tingkat dengan seni dan musik asli. SIM BSD."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— A cyberpunk total conversion with new weapons, enemies, and levels. Standalone v1.2 IWAD. Freeware."
msgstr "- Sebuah cyberpunk total konversi dengan senjata baru, musuh, dan tingkat. Standalone v1.2 IWAD. Freeware."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:120
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Adventure games reward thorough exploration. Look at, pick up, and talk to everything you can."
msgstr "- Petualangan permainan penghargaan eksplorasi menyeluruh. Lihatlah, angkat, dan berbicara dengan segala sesuatu yang Anda bisa."

