msgstr "- PrBoom + dikompile ke WebAssembly via Emscripten (GPL-2.0). Mendukung WAD, PWAD, patch DEH/BEX, sintesis OPL, masukan gamepad, dan perekaman widecreen."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_freedoom1.html.heex:83
